  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kdemultimedia</title>

    <para>This package provides multimedia applications for KDE, such as a 
    mixer, video player (Dragon), audio player (JuK) and CD player (Kscd).</para>

    &lfs71_checked;

